---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---
<ContentSection title="Who this is for" id="intro">
  <Icon slot="eyebrow" name="mdi:briefcase-outline" class="size-16" />

  <Fragment slot="lead">
    This is for business owners who already know their financial world is too
    fragmented — and want one clear point of strategic oversight.
  </Fragment>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center space-y-4 text-lg text-text-offset">
    <p>
      If your accounting, tax planning, reporting, and long-term financial
      decisions all live in different places, clarity gets lost.
    </p>
    <p>
      We work with established owners who don’t need convincing —
      they need coordination, confidence, and a trusted advisor who sees
      the full picture.
    </p>
  </div>
</ContentSection>


